		"name": "MedManage API - Complete Test Suite",
		"description": "Comprehensive test suite for MedManage API endpoints covering Member, Case, and ServiceProvider entities.\n\nIncludes:\n- Member CRUD Operations\n- Case CRUD Operations\n- Service Provider CRUD Operations\n- Validation Tests\n- Performance Tests\n- Soft delete functionality\n- Audit trail verification\n\nRun with Newman: newman run MedManage.postman_collection.json -e MedManage.postman_environment.json",
